{"tid":1460541,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[劉勝華輔警扮記者] 吳文遠散播fake news","createTime":"2019-08-13T03:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T03:33:34.000Z","uid":179232,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86b04026399bb7ec9980d046dc7b153181a742e3","tid":1460541,"uid":179232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:30:45.000Z","msg":"事源係有人喺機場影到有個記者同個警察好似樣, 就出現咗依張圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9L7C11D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9L7C11D.jpg&h=4bbe7699&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後就有人話著白衫嗰張圖係寒戰劇照, 吳文遠未fact check就話劉勝華只係臨時演員, 係外國記者既助手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GLzh14g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGLzh14g.jpg&h=5c550e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0ERm4h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0ERm4h.jpg&h=9fcd36bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我翻查資料, 劉勝華係退役英軍, 做緊輔警工作<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PDDlpFGhR_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPDDlpFGhR_8&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y98emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=e4a77685\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PDDlpFGhR_8</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">劉勝華接受英國華人職業傳承史項目的採訪。劉勝華於1987年加入香港軍事服務團 (HKMSC)，隨後派往皇家陸軍獸科兵團 (RAVC)為領犬員，稍後調往皇家香港軍團 (RHKR)為特擊隊小隊副指揮，服務至1995年皇家香港軍團 (RHKR)解散。離開軍隊後，他參加了皇家香港輔助警察(RHKAP)，目前也是華籍英兵樂善會(BCSBA)的委員。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20121632/cgn201216325323.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20121632%2Fcgn201216325323.pdf&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y98emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=299dbeff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20121632/cgn201216325323.pdf</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">16. 劉勝華  編號: 6559  警長(輔警)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望吳文遠盡快澄清, 以正視聽<br />\n<br />\n#黑警死全家"},{"pid":"ae59d84da9be00ffebef5c587fb64280154f14d2","tid":1460541,"uid":263260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:32:02.000Z","msg":"輔警來，常屌示威者搞事"},{"pid":"04b6737e2ab702e75e2d98c0c5774fa44c83bb4d","tid":1460541,"uid":102981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"好多轉左行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba35efe2e91b50bd3b17245c0b59ba814aae8df","tid":1460541,"uid":70336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"不推文回覆"}]}